4. 
Scanning Process
Types:
1.Passive Scanning


Client listens for Beacon frames


No transmission


Slower but power efficient


2.Active Scanning


Client sends Probe Request


AP replies with Probe Response


Faster

Steps:
Scan channels
Discover APs
Select best AP (RSSI, load)


