7.
 Power Saving Mechanism
Goal:
Save battery

Steps:


1.Client sends QoS NULL (sleep)
2.AP buffers data
3.AP sends Beacon (TIM/DTIM)
4.Client checks PVB (bitmap)
5.If data → sends PS-Poll
6.AP sends data

Types:

Legacy Power Save
U-APSD (WMM Power Save)



