9. 
Block ACK Mechanism
Purpose:
Reduce ACK overhead
Instead of:
ACK for each frame 
Use:
One ACK for multiple frames 

Types:

Immediate Block ACK
Delayed Block ACK


Advantages:
Higher throughput
Less overhead
Efficient retransmission



10.
A-MSDU, A-MPDU, A-MSDU in A-MPDU

A-MSDU:
Multiple MSDUs inside one MAC frame
One MAC header
If error → retransmit entire frame


A-MPDU:
Multiple MPDUs aggregated
Each subframe has its own MAC header
Retransmit only failed frames using sequence number

A-MSDU inside A-MPDU:
Combination of both
Maximum efficiency
Reduced overhead


